Context: This string serves as a tab title for a script diff view of a single script. The argument will be a script path/name.
This string serves as a tab title for a script diff view of multiple scripts. The argument will be a number indicating how many scripts are being diffed in this tab.

Source: Review the changes and click '%1' to apply them to your script
